          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "You can't know it through your feelings or your circumstances-those lie to you. You know it through His word and the fruit in your life. Matthew 28:20 says \"I am with you always.\" That's the promise. The fruit-love, joy, peace, patience-is the evidence that it's real. Start looking for the small mercies instead of waiting for a miracle. The ride home you caught. The money you didn't steal. The sickness that didn't kill you. These are proof. Your feelings will catch up eventually, but don't wait for them. Trust the word and the fruit."
